Question 3.3

Fibonacci <- numeric(12)
Fibonacci[1] <- 1
Fibonacci[2] <- 1
for (x in 3:12) Fibonacci[x] <- Fibonacci[x-2] + Fibonacci[x-1]
print("First 12 Fibonacci numbers:")
## [1] "First 12 Fibonacci numbers:"
print(Fibonacci)
